Sentencas: La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 powders were prepared by liquid-solid reaction method using humidified (3 % H2O) hydrogen as fuel and ambient air as oxidant.
Titulo: Liquid-Solid Reaction Method to Synthesize La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 Powder as Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: These powders were evaluated in terms of phase structure, morphology and fuel cell performances.
Titulo: Liquid-Solid Reaction Method to Synthesize La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 Powder as Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: An electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cell was prepared in a conventional manner.
Titulo: Liquid-Solid Reaction Method to Synthesize La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 Powder as Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The results showed that the formation of La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 perovskite phase was acquired at 1100 degrees C for 5 h. The particles of the powders were uniform and were about 0.1-0.3 mu m.
Titulo: Liquid-Solid Reaction Method to Synthesize La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 Powder as Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: At 750 degrees C, the maximum power density of a single cell with La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 powder were 135 mW cm(-2).
Titulo: Liquid-Solid Reaction Method to Synthesize La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 Powder as Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell
